column5: Has any body been out to Whitemouth lake yet ice fishing. i have heard rumors people are out

I have no idea whether people have been out there yet. I do believe that the ice would be safe for snowmobiles and 4-wheelers, but I would not trust it for driving my vehicle out there, it's been a little to warm this fall.
Are there any fish left in the lake?

I've only fished there a couple times, just to try it, we didn't do very good at all, but the conservation officer stopped by and said that some guys were doing pretty good on a different part of the lake. Guess you just have to know where to go.
contacts tell me they have been catching...for up to date reports go towww.members3.boardhost.com/fishmanitoba/seems like the lake keeps ticking and ticking
